Package: CircularRegression
Type: Package
Title: Circular Regression Models
Version: 0.1.1
Authors@R: c(
    person( "Aurelien", "Nicosia",
           email = "aurelien.nicosia@mat.ulaval.ca",
           role = c("aut", "cre")))
Description: This package implements various regression models for analyzing 
    circular data. The package provides 
    implementations of models such as the angular regression model, the consensus 
    model, the decentered predictor model, and the Presnell model.
